{"tid":2418991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"數十萬人上街 企業響應大罷工  民不懼死 緬甸掀22222革命","createTime":"2021-02-23T04:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T06:08:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5c134c42088f06e3b1916fcde72dd2f8b7f648cf","tid":2418991,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T04:28:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210223/HRSNAKYFCBFSZBITN475FHM5TQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210223%2FHRSNAKYFCBFSZBITN475FHM5TQ%2F&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=e81ff919\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210223%2FHRSNAKYFCBFSZBITN475FHM5TQ%2F&h=298c0401\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210223/HRSNAKYFCBFSZBITN475FHM5TQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n數十萬人上街 企業響應大罷工 <br />\n民不懼死 緬甸掀22222革命<br />\n<br />\n緬甸民眾越受打壓越是頑強，面對軍方周末奪走三命後再發出毫不含蓄的死亡威脅，緬甸人拒絕被嚇怕，數以十萬計人昨日繼續上街堅決反對政變外，大小企業亦響應罷工，昨紛紛休息一天。重視吉祥日子的緬甸人都期望2021年2月22日是好日子，會成為「22222革命」或「春天革命」邁向勝利的轉捩點。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：東盟走後門斡旋 促軍政府停鎮壓<br />\n<br />\n雖然軍方前日深夜透過國營電視台MRTV發出警告，指「示威者煽動民眾、特別是情緒化的年輕人，走上對抗之路，他們將要面對人命損失」，表明準備好用致命武力對應「無政府狀態」，警告民眾昨天勿罷工，但無法嚇倒民眾，在仰光、內比都、曼德勒、密支那和土瓦等至少十多個城市昨日繼續舉行和平集會，要求釋放被捕的國務資政昂山素姬。<br />\n<br />\n在首都內比都，警方很快就採取行動驅散群眾。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：央行高層地震 危及5,850億元經濟<br />\n<br />\n在最大城市仰光，使館區是主要聚集地區，昨天一早通向美國等大使館的道路都被封，有坐滿20輛車的防暴警察在場候命。但一早仍有成千上萬人走出來。46歲的山山莫說：「大家都加入了。我們必須出來。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IjupxJU_yBtMALkc1zcdnYOaEDw=/3150x2100/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GC57RMG2FZGRXFAZIHWK6NCKSM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIjupxJU_yBtMALkc1zcdnYOaEDw%3D%2F3150x2100%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGC57RMG2FZGRXFAZIHWK6NCKSM.jpg&h=f899061a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■和平示威者把曼德勒一條大街擠得水洩不通。法新社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n擇「五條二」吉日 冀成轉捩點<br />\n<br />\n緬甸人向來重視吉祥日子，昨天日期集合了五個二字，他們認為別具意義，不少人將之與1988年8月8日爭取民主的示威相提並論；儘管「8888民運」遭血腥鎮壓，民間估計整場運動或有上萬人喪生。<br />\n<br />\n相比當年軍方今次似乎較克制。由本月1日政變，三周以來民眾示威與公民抗命運動每日上演，但軍方耐性正消失。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n示威者害怕也是常情。22歲的泰泰蘭坦言憂懼，因此出門示威前先誠心祈禱。她說：「我們要民主不要軍政府，我們要創造自己的未來。媽媽也沒有阻止我，只叮囑我當心。」23歲大學生覺覺也矢言會堅持抗爭直至勝利。「我們害怕鎮壓，但我們必須向前。我們真的很憤怒。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學者：和平解決窗口漸關上<br />\n<br />\n這股義憤亦令公民抗命運動規模有增無已。昨日罷工行動參與的有。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n歷史學者丹敏吳（Thant Myint U）認為局勢不樂觀，和平化解危機的窗口已漸漸關上：「。。。。。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n路透社/法新社/美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LW4cS6p0rfAP5qhk0Zy5yC1iZmw=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LE6IMBCBF5EM3EJ7ZJWMUVU4EM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLW4cS6p0rfAP5qhk0Zy5yC1iZmw%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLE6IMBCBF5EM3EJ7ZJWMUVU4EM.jpg&h=708dc14d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■受到軍方恐嚇的仰光市民，昨日繼續走上街頭。法新社"},{"pid":"018229bb0a65399d7826aea37200bb8289d571ea","tid":2418991,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T04:29:24.000Z","msg":"加油呀緬甸人民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c6dde0011e00245105f7104dba275657e3834d","tid":2418991,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T05:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUOWpYB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUOWpYB.png&h=cf5cca57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有冇人知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37d9f4b2975b277878357a54be3eca64cd7bd62","tid":2418991,"uid":125945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T05:34:20.000Z","msg":"如果香港人可以這樣就好了！希望緬甸成功！"},{"pid":"b36608df79d922e8685452e5508eb9a94e659186","tid":2418991,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b21928d2795a32d8a9505c8c2db853d4c048f23","tid":2418991,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cbb4de3290d8292ce1cd9bfa27a8ad74c3a80b","tid":2418991,"uid":107419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:03:23.000Z","msg":"光復緬甸，時代革命。<br />\n黑軍警死全家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3acae5f9ab6e980e2ccf8bdde91f595c55bf8cab","tid":2418991,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6p8GARS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6p8GARS.jpg&h=a77d7a83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a13a417f42a92b9c16d4a4e72c289919d012cdc","tid":2418991,"uid":347528,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:08:10.000Z","msg":"香港人就係怕死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}